cs.DC, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.PL

This paper deals with the placement of virtual components in data centers to optimize network performance. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also addresses network resource demands, which suggests the category cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The optimization problem and proposed heuristic algorithm fall under the category cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also deals with composite applications, which suggests the category cs.SE (Software Engineering). Finally, the paper proposes a greedy heuristic algorithm, which falls under the category cs.PL (Programming Languages).
